{"id":491917332,"lang":"java","time":"9 months, 3 weeks","timestamp":1620769274,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"8 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/491917332/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Reverse Vowels of a String","memory":"40.4 MB","code":"class Solution {\n    public String reverseVowels(String s) {\n        int start = 0, end = s.length() - 1;\n        String vowels = \"aeiouAEIOU\";\n        char[] chars = s.toCharArray();\n        while (start < end) {\n            while (start<end && !vowels.contains(chars[start]+\"\")) start++;\n            while (start<end && !vowels.contains(chars[end]+\"\")) end--;\n            char temp = chars[start];\n            chars[start] = chars[end];\n            chars[end] = temp;\n            start++;\n            end--;\n        }\n        return String.valueOf(chars);\n    }\n}","compare_result":"","title_slug":"reverse-vowels-of-a-string"}
